    "description": "<strong>A Pigeon Detective Game: Twin Beaks</strong> is a murder-mystery novel game set in an idyllic tourist village. Meet the prime suspects as you question them about their alibis, and gather all of their saucy secrets. Your case seems simple, a body found at dawn belonging to the village's delivery pigeon, <i>Bobert Squab</i>... yet what lies underneath this humble town is darkness and intrigue.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Branching and Unlockable Dialogue</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Meet and interview your suspects, unlocking dialogue as you find out more info from other pigeons and the environment around you.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875230/extras/434c58b3a84dba69275869103ad04623.poster.avif?t=1714476039\" width=518 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875230/extras/434c58b3a84dba69275869103ad04623.webm?t=1714476039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875230/extras/434c58b3a84dba69275869103ad04623.mp4?t=1714476039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Open World</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore in a 3rd-person perspective as you rollerskate around the village of Twin Beaks.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875230/extras/c70ce84beabdca343ded3109c190287f.poster.avif?t=1714476039\" width=518 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875230/extras/c70ce84beabdca343ded3109c190287f.webm?t=1714476039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875230/extras/c70ce84beabdca343ded3109c190287f.mp4?t=1714476039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You alone have the power to find out what really happened that fateful night, and bring the right pigeon to justice!",
